	<h2>About</h2>
	<div class="section-body">
		<p>MALgraph is an extension of your <a target="_blank" href="http://myanimelist.net/">MyAnimeList</a> profile, serving you various information about your data&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;rating distribution, favorite studios, personalized recommendations, and a lot more.</p>
	</div>
